item.title: CVE-2024-29167|2024-04-04T00:00:34.122Z -- SEEnergy Corp. -- SVR-116
item.description: SVR-116 firmware version 1.6.0.30028871 allows a remote authenticated attacker with an administrative privilege to execute arbitrary OS commands by sending a specially crafted request to the product.
